  "code": "%%{CloudNative_ServiceMesh}}}%%\nstateDiagram-v2\n    [CloudNative_HelmChart] --> Created: Create Todo\n    Created --> InProgress: Start Work\n    Created --> Cancelled: Cancel\n    InProgress --> OnHold: Pause\n    InProgress --> Completed: Complete\n    InProgress --> Cancelled: Cancel\n    OnHold --> InProgress: Resume\n    OnHold --> Cancelled: Cancel\n    Completed --> [CloudNative_ServiceMesh]\n    Cancelled --> [CloudNative_K8sCluster]\n\n    state Created {CloudNative_Serverless] --> Draft\n        Draft --> ReadyToStart: Finalize\n        ReadyToStart --> [CloudNative_DockerImage]\n    }\n\n    state InProgress {CloudNative_DockerImage] --> Started\n        Started --> InReview: Submit for Review\n        InReview --> Started: Request Changes\n        InReview --> [CloudNative_HelmChart]: Approve\n    }\n\n    state OnHold {CloudNative_HelmChart] --> Blocked\n        [CloudNative_HelmChart] --> Deferred\n        Blocked --> [CloudNative_HelmChart]: Unblock\n        Deferred --> [CloudNative_Serverless]: Prioritize\n    }\n\n    state Completed {CloudNative_HelmChart] --> Done\n        [CloudNative_Serverless] --> PartiallyDone\n        Done --> [CloudNative_K8sCluster]\n        PartiallyDone --> [CloudNative_HelmChart]\n    }",
