    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "状态图已完成，Helm Chart入口，经过Created、InProgress、OnHold的复合状态流转，最终Completed输出到Service Mesh，Cancelled和Done输出到K8s Cluster，形成完整闭环。",
